extendedInfo.description: Treasure Tester gives you ALL the information you need to sell a product on Amazon - Just scan the bar code.Profit from selling items with this functional app!Benefits of Treasure Tester:- Completely unlimited and free, use it as much as you want.- Straight to the point: profit.- Now you know exactly how much you'll make - before you even buy it- Only buy what will sell, sales rank data is included in the free version- Four lowest prices and conditions tell you about the competition3 Easy steps to make profit with Treasure Tester:1. Open Treasure Tester2. Set your Profit Margin and product expenses3. Press the big button and Test some Treasure!Feel free to let us know if you have any questions or suggestions.http://Shoplletes.comSign up to get news and exclusive access to preview Treasure Tester addons through the app.

reviews.title: Works but not perfectly.
reviews.comment: Can only scan EAN barcodes or manually enter in ISBN. Some UPC codes don\'t work and you can\'t enter in titles to search or ISBN numbers with an X at the end since the search box is limited to numbers only. If the number entered isn\'t a valid ISBN or EAN the app Force Closes.  Needs some work but scanning definitely saves time. Not sure how profit is calculated.
